	<h2><u>Birth :</u></h2>
	<p>Arjuna was the son of Indra, the king of the celestials, born of Kunti, the first wife of King Pandu in the Kuru Kingdom.</br>
		Arjuna was trained in religion, science, administration and military arts by Bhishma & Drona.</p>
