<h4><strong>Death:</strong></h4>
<p>Except for Yudhishthira, all of the Pandavas grew weak and died before reaching heaven (only Yudhishthira is allowed to keep his mortal body).</br> Arjuna was the fourth one to fall after Draupadi, Sahadeva and Nakula.</p>
